Wigan got goals from Jordi Gomez and
Hugo Rodallega to defeat Wolves at home to move out of the
relegation zone of Englandâ€™s top soccer division.  Gomez scored with a free kick in the 65th minute and
Rodallega took advantage of poor defending to grab the second in
85th minute. Wolves captain Karl Henry was dismissed in the
